Really? That's really nice, isn't it? That's really nice of them

153
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:35,860
Flags are used to mark where
the main road runs through the camp

154
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,520
The camp covers a sizeable area of the glacier

155
00:12:38,529 --> 00:12:43,100
And the staff use a multitude of vehicles to to move equipment and travel from one part to another

156
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:47,040
This is a Ski-Doo

157
