provide wind and weather updates to flight crews

174
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:48,870
climbers and expeditions on the ice.

175
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:51,760
Everyday Celine receives a new weather update

176
00:14:51,770 --> 00:14:54,990
it's the same weather information
the crew of the Ilyushin are using in Chile

177
