For the first flight of the season

178
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:01,220
the pilot won't fly unless the
conditions are perfect

179
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,120
He needs good visibility

180
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,300
 good contrast

181
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:05,920
and low wind speeds

182
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:08,800
and he also won't want the Sun in his eyes when approaching the runway

183
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,940
Which rules out a night flight

184
