The camp can house just over 100 people
at any time

197
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:04,830
and is made of a PolarHaven tents most
of them need to be assembled from scratch

198
00:16:04,830 --> 00:16:08,650
but a few left intact over winter these
need to be dug out

199
00:16:08,650 --> 00:16:11,330
and shifted into the right position

200
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:29,470
Until the weather improves

201
00:16:29,470 --> 00:16:32,790
there will be no fresh food deliveries
and the camp will need to be set-up

202
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:35,410
