provides electricity for the staff and clients

213
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:42,979
these panels also supply energy to the snow melters in order to make hot water for cooking

214
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:46,419
And to strengthen the tents against strong winds

215
00:17:46,419 --> 00:17:50,499
deep holes are drilled into the snow to secure guide ropes

