when a new Antarctic Treaty is drawn up
it will change the continent and the way we see it forever

412
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:29,300
Antarctica has been free of conflict and aggression

413
00:41:29,329 --> 00:41:34,400
in a way that other parts of the world
have always desired. It has been a shelter for knowledge

414
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:37,880
