deeds and struggles

416
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:45,040
despite being so remote, so barren and
stark

417
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:48,990
It has become entangled in the search for
individual meaning and self-knowledge

418
00:41:48,990 --> 00:41:52,160
amidst a fetish for exploration and
discovery

419
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:56,180
